column2: SELECT f.ra, f.dec, f.plate, f.mjd, f.fiberid, f.specobjid, f.bestobjid, s.teffadop, s.fehadop, s.loggadop, sp.subclass, s.SPECTYPEHAMMER, s.spectypesubclass, s.TEFFIRFM, s.LOGGNGS1IRFM, s.FEHNGS1IRFM, s.teffspec, s.loggspec, s.fehspec, s.flag into mydb.segue_crosschecked_#_flags from myDB.flaretable_crosscheck_sdss_specobj as f JOIN sppParams as s ON f.specobjid = s.specobjid join specobjall as sp on f.specobjid = sp.specobjid
